public class DBExtendedTypeCode
extends java.lang.Object

THIS CLASS IS CURRENTLY NOT USED AND THEREFORE ITS INTERFACE CANNOT BE GUARENTEED The DBExtendedTypeCode class serves as the interface layer to the ExtendedTypeCode table in the database for the relationship between ExtendedNodeTypes and Codes in the datamodel.
